body:
So with the new lore of Jhin coming out, we get a greater look into {{champion:238}} and {{champion:98}}&#039;s history. In the champion Q&amp;A thread I remember a Red stating that, &quot;Jhin is the actual bad guy within Zed and Shen&#039;s story, not Zed.&quot;

So I have question about that:

If Shen and Zed&#039;s lore get updated, will they no longer be bitter rivals, but instead just acquaintances? Zed still killed his master so obviously Shen will hold some resentment towards him, but the Eye of Twilight must &quot;hold no emotion to acquire equilibrium.&quot; In other words, will Zed and Shen have to team up to stop Jhin and &quot;enforce balance&quot;?
